Invocation Name: christmas spectacular
des:
Now it’s easier than ever to learn about the legendary Radio City Rockettes. Just ask Alexa!

Make the Christmas Spectacular part of your holiday tradition, and experience the kinds of moments that memories are made of. Every year, the Christmas Spectacular comes to life as Radio City® transforms into an immersive, magical wonderland!

Enable the Skill and get started by saying “Alexa, open Christmas Spectacular.” You can also say “Alexa, ask Christmas Spectacular for a fun fact.”
 
Learn more about the Christmas Spectacular at https://www.rockettes.com/christmas/
